OL,3,CMurdered woman's mother welcomes call
OL,4,Cto rethink killer's release
OL,6,FThe mother of a woman who was raped
OL,7,Fand murdered in Northumberland has
OL,8,Fbacked a call from the Lord Chancellor
OL,9,Fto reconsider the recommendation to
OL,10,Frelease her daughter's killer.
OL,12,FSteven Ling has served 27 years in
OL,13,Fprison after he was jailed for life
OL,14,Fafter admitting to the murder of 29-
OL,15,Fyear-old Joanne Tulip in Stamfordham
OL,16,Fin 1997.
