OL,3,CMurdered woman's mother welcomes call
OL,4,Cto rethink killer's release
OL,6,FJoanne's mother Doreen Soulsby said:
OL,7,F"I welcome the decision taken by the
OL,8,FSecretary of State for Justice to
OL,9,Fsubmit a reconsideration request to
OL,10,Fthe Parole Board.
OL,12,F"I strongly disagreed with the Parole
OL,13,FBoard's decision to release Ling
OL,14,Fstraight into the community.
OL,16,F"This is a man who committed the most
OL,17,Fhorrific sadistic crimes against my
OL,18,Fdaughter, including stabbing her 60
OL,19,Ftimes and raping her, after having
OL,20,Fconsumed a significant amount of
OL,21,Falcohol.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/7
