OL,3,CMurdered woman's mother welcomes call
OL,4,Cto rethink killer's release
OL,6,F"Ling has spent 27 years in custody
OL,7,Fwithout having had sex. There is a
OL,8,Fpossibility that once he is let out in
OL,9,Fthe community, he will seriously harm
OL,10,Fother women and will use force to do
OL,11,Fso, as he did with Joanne.
OL,13,F"There is nothing that can be done to
OL,14,Fstop this man constantly thinking he
OL,15,Fis entitled to sex."
OL,17,FLing, a farm worker, was inspired to
OL,18,Fmurder Ms Tulip on Christmas Day 1997
OL,19,Fby sadism, Newcastle Crown Court heard
OL,20,Fat the time.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/7
