OL,4,Cto rethink killer's release
OL,6,F"Public protection is my first
OL,7,Fpriority. After careful consideration,
OL,8,FI have asked the Parole Board to
OL,9,Freconsider its decision to release
OL,10,FSteven Ling from prison."
